data.description: Do not miss out on this well-maintained spacious 4-SIDED BRICK home offering 4 Bedrooms and 3 Full Baths. The two-story foyer entryway and towering ceilings of the primary living area with high-set windows allow natural light to flow through the home.  A bonus is the one bedroom on the main level with a full bath providing a convenient floor plan for guests or family members wishing to avoid the stairs. The upper floor features an oversized master with an extended seating area, tray ceilings, his and her closets, a master bath with a separate shower/garden tub, and double vanities. Two additional spacious bedrooms upstairs share a full bath.  And there is the loft landing overlooking the main living area and front entry foyer.  Recently installed hardwood floors throughout the home. Home is located near HWY 124/Scenic Hwy, 316, I-85, The Shoppes at Webb Ginn for your shopping trips, and numerous restaurants for great dining experiences. This home is ideal for 1st time home buyers, owner occupant/s, or rental investment - as the HOA is low and there is NO RENTAL RESTRICTION! You must have a confirmed appointment to show.
